Shalamar performing A Night To Remember (M&M Remix).

"A Night to Remember" is a song by American R&B group Shalamar, which has been remixed by John Morales (also known as M&M) and released in the year 1986. The song was originally written by Nidra Beard of Dynasty, Dana Meyers and Charmaine Sylvers of the Sylvers.

